00:06:03,340 --> 00:06:04,180
Čo sa to deje?

60
00:06:04,220 --> 00:06:04,900
Poď sem!

61
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:08,220
Koľkokrát ti to mám ešte povedať?!

62
00:06:08,940 --> 00:06:10,520
Prestaň sa s tým deckom stretávať.

63
00:06:17,900 --> 00:06:19,400
Nie!

64
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:20,900
Nie!

65
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,400
Vypadni!

66
00:06:22,400 --> 00:06:23,900
Povedal som, vypadni!

67
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:28,400
Parm, neboj sa.

68
00:06:29,200 --> 00:06:29,900
Neboj sa.

69
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:32,900
Nič sa nedeje, Parm.

70
00:06:33,900 --> 00:06:35,900
Parm, neboj sa.

71
00:06:39,800 --> 00:06:40,400
Neboj sa.

72
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:41,900
Všetko je v poriadku.

73
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:43,900
Ten muž.

74
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:45,400
Ten muž...

75
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:47,400
Už nechcem...

76
00:06:47,400 --> 00:06:50,040
Už to nechcem vidieť!

77
00:06:50,520 --> 00:06:51,420
Upokoj sa, Parm.

78
00:06:51,420 --> 00:06:52,900
Vypadni!

79
00:07:00,700 --> 00:07:01,540
Korn!

80
00:07:03,900 --> 00:07:04,400
Nie.

81
00:07:04,400 --> 00:07:05,180
Korn!

82
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,020
Nerob to!

