00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:08,400
Korn!

84
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,100
Parm!

85
00:07:10,620 --> 00:07:11,720
Parm.

86
00:07:11,780 --> 00:07:12,900
Počkaj.

87
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:14,080
Ja to vyriešim.

88
00:07:27,240 --> 00:07:29,920
Nikto vás nechce rozdeliť.

89
00:07:55,300 --> 00:07:56,040
Intouch.

90
00:07:59,900 --> 00:08:02,860
Tvoj rodičia veľmi dlho trpeli.

91
00:08:07,900 --> 00:08:09,400
Tento byt...

92
00:08:09,900 --> 00:08:10,900
Nie.

93
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,400
Táto celá bytovka...

94
00:08:17,340 --> 00:08:19,000
Otec ju kúpil pre vás dvoch.

95
00:08:22,900 --> 00:08:25,840
Udržiavame to tu stále tak,

96
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:30,880
ako to bolo pred tridsiatimi rokmi.

97
00:08:38,500 --> 00:08:40,140
Tvoj otec,

98
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,900
strážil vaše spomienky.

99
00:08:57,680 --> 00:09:00,580
Otec ťa veľmi miluje
a chýbal si mu, Korn.

100
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:07,460
Vždy keď sa pozrie na tú krabicu...

101
00:09:10,340 --> 00:09:13,900
začne plakať.

102
00:09:20,460 --> 00:09:21,280
Intouch.

103
00:09:23,900 --> 00:09:26,220
Aj tvoj otec za tebou smútil.

104
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,900
Neskutočne dlho plakal.

105
00:09:35,900 --> 00:09:39,680
Plakal, akoby sa mu zrútil celý svet.

106
00:09:46,100 --> 00:09:48,100
Otec.

107
00:09:50,580 --> 00:09:53,100
Prepáč.

108
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:10,300
Je to moja vina.

109
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:14,720
Všetkým okolo mňa som ublížil.

110
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:24,440
Prepáčte.

111
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:26,540
Otec.

112
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,120
Korn.

113
00:10:51,300 --> 00:10:52,800
Po tom pohrebe...

114
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:57,620
sme nikdy nestratili kontakt
s Intouch-ovou rodinou.

115
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:02,620
Keď Intouch-ov otec ochorel,

116
00:11:02,740 --> 00:11:04,620
vedeli sme, že nás čoskoro opustí.

117
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:09,300
Náš otec mu sľúbil,

118
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:14,000
že sa bude navždy starať o Intouch-ovu rodinu.

119
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,820
Robí tak doteraz.

120
00:11:19,780 --> 00:11:21,740
Navždy.

121
00:11:30,380 --> 00:11:32,300
Už sa na nášho otca nehnevaj.

122
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,140
In, už sa prestaň hnevať.

123
00:11:41,740 --> 00:11:44,260
Všetci sme niekoľko rokov trpeli.

124
00:11:48,460 --> 00:11:52,940
Kard sa na otca hneval
a nikdy mu neodpustil.

125
00:11:54,940 --> 00:11:57,540
Aj keď bol na smrteľnej posteli...

126
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:02,780
Odmietol sa stretnúť s otcom.

127
00:12:12,300 --> 00:12:13,940
Prepáč.

128
00:12:15,940 --> 00:12:17,380
To všetko kvôli mne.

129
00:12:19,140 --> 00:12:21,500
Všetkým som veľmi ublížil.

130
00:12:23,300 --> 00:12:24,860
Bol som hlúpy.

131
00:12:29,300 --> 00:12:30,960
Bol som sebecký.

132
00:12:35,160 --> 00:12:35,980
Ale teraz...

133
00:12:40,700 --> 00:12:42,300
Teraz všetkých ľúbim.

134
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,300
Ľúbim ťa, otec.

135
00:12:47,300 --> 00:12:48,300
A aj mamu.

136
00:12:50,700 --> 00:12:52,480
Ľúbim všetkých mojich bratov.

137
00:12:55,900 --> 00:12:58,060
A neskutočne ťa milujem, In.

138
00:13:23,280 --> 00:13:24,800
Prepáč, In.

139
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:27,880
Odpusť mi.

140
00:13:29,300 --> 00:13:30,900
Prepáč.

141
00:14:10,800 --> 00:14:11,800
Intouch...

142
00:14:14,520 --> 00:14:16,440
Myslel si,
že si bol veľmi silný.

143
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,280
Tvoj dáždnik...

144
00:14:24,040 --> 00:14:25,900
je veľký a ťažký.

145
00:14:26,700 --> 00:14:28,640
Môj dáždnik je oveľa lepší.

146
00:14:31,540 --> 00:14:33,060
Postarám sa o teba.

147
00:14:50,200 --> 00:14:51,400
Prepáč.

148
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:59,440
Prepáč, že som hodil
všetku vinu na teba.

149
00:15:06,700 --> 00:15:08,360
Milujem ťa.

150
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:14,700
Odpúšťam ti.

151
00:15:17,530 --> 00:15:19,710
Už sa nemusíš obviňovať.

152
00:16:01,770 --> 00:16:03,650
Aj ja ťa milujem, In.

153
00:16:05,150 --> 00:16:06,500
Neskutočne ťa milujem.

